1. Ja sam sinoć čistio *kupatilo* i sada je besprekorno čisto. (I cleaned the *bathroom* last night and now it's spotless.)
2. Potrebna su mi nova vrata za *kupatilo*. (I need new doors for the *bathroom*.)
3. *Kupatilo* je najmanja soba u stanu, ali je veoma važno. (The *bathroom* is the smallest room in the apartment, but it's very important.)
4. Da li si video novi set peškira u *kupatilu*? (Did you see the new set of towels in the *bathroom*?)
5. U *kupatilu* se osećam opušteno i relaksirano. (I feel relaxed and at ease in the *bathroom*.)
6. Kada sam ušao u *kupatilo*, primetio sam da je ostavljena upaljena svetlost. (When I entered the *bathroom*, I noticed that the light was left on.)
7. Ovo *kupatilo* je renovirano pre godinu dana. (This *bathroom* was renovated a year ago.)
8. Treba mi nova ogledala za *kupatilo*. (I need new mirrors for the *bathroom*.)
9. U *kupatilu* se ne sme pušiti. (Smoking is not allowed in the *bathroom*.)
10. Kada budem imao svoju kuću, želim da imam veliko *kupatilo*. (When I have my own house, I want to have a big *bathroom*.)